by Leskya » Mon Oct 12, 2020 12:57 pm

Although blades are weapons used by Ghesites during combat, their cultural significance is much more than mere battle equipment. The style and utility of a knife has social status attached to it, and knives are used in pretty much every role within Ghesite society. The scarcity of bronze within the nomadic society grants it almost a luxurious status - explaining why Ari has a weird fetish for them; as the Caller, she is increasingly more considered to be the paramount leader of the Ghesites.
